title: What's behind the peace negotiations for Ukraine?, by Thierry Meyssan
description: We don't know what was said in Washington, but we can assume that the United States took a firm stance toward Ukraine, even if it didn't want to risk destroying Atlantic solidarity. Thierry Meyssan presents here what transpired during this tumultuous week.
